   "source": [
    "# Phase 2 — RNN Model (Full Samanantar Dataset)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key changes from Phase 1:\n",
    "- **ChunkedTranslationDataset**: reads processed CSV chunks lazily instead of loading one huge pickle\n",
    "- **Batch size raised** to 256 to better utilise the university GPU\n",
    "- **pin_memory=True + num_workers=4** on DataLoaders for faster GPU data transfer\n",
    "- **Checkpoint saving every epoch** (not just best) so training can resume after a server timeout\n",
    "- **Resume-from-checkpoint** logic at the top of the training loop\n",
    "- **BLEU, ChrF, COMET, BERTScore** evaluation metrics (same set as Phase 2 goal)\n",
    "- DATA_DIR points to the output of Phase2_Preprocessing_NN.ipynb"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
